<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>

    <head>
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' charset='UTF-8'/>

        {% block stylesheets %}
            {{ include('@SyliusWeb/_stylesheets.html.twig') }}
        {% endblock %}

        <title>CJ-MaX {% block title %}{% endblock %}</title>
    </head>

    <body>
        {% block header %}
            {% block navbar %}
                {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/_navbar.html.twig') }}
            {% endblock %}
        {% endblock %}

        <div class="container">
            <div id="topbar" class="col-md-12">
                {% block topbar %}
                {% endblock %}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="flashes" class="col-md-12">
            {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/_flashes.html.twig') }}

            {% block flashes %}
            {% endblock %}
        </div>
        <div id="all">
            {% block content %}
                {% block carousel %}
                    {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/Homepage/_carousel.html.twig') }}
                {% endblock %}
                <div id="content">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="col-sm-12">
                            <div class="box text-center">
                                <h3 class="text-uppercase">New and popular products</h3>
                                <h4 class="text-muted"><span class="accent">Free shipping</span> on everything</h4>
                            </div>
                            {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/Product/_productGrid.html.twig') }}
                            <div class="same-height-row row grid-items gi-categories">
                                {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/Product/categories.html.twig') }}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bar background-image-fixed-2 no-mb color-white text-center">
                        <div class="dark-mask"></div>
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                    <div class="icon icon-lg"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-question-circle"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h1>What are you looking for today?</h1>
                                    <p class="lead">Ask us anything - we're here to help!</p>
                                    <form role="search">
                                        <div class="input-group">
                                            <input type="text" placeholder="Type your query here" class="form-control">
                                        <span class="input-group-btn">
                                            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
                                        </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="col-sm-12">
                            <div class="box text-center">
                                <h3 class="text-uppercase">From our blog</h3>

                                <p class="text-italic text-large">What's new in the world of fashion? <span class="accent">Check our blog!</span>
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <div id="blog-homepage" class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-6">
                                    <div class="post">
                                        <h4><a href="#">Fashion now</a></h4>
                                        <p class="author-category">By <a href="#">John Slim</a> in <a href="">Fashion and style</a>
                                        </p>
                                        <hr>
                                        <p class="intro">Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Vestibulum tortor quam, feugiat vitae, ultricies eget, tempor sit amet, ante. Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean
                                            ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo.</p>
                                        <p class="read-more"><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Continue reading</a>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="col-sm-6">
                                    <div class="post">
                                        <h4><a href="#">Who is who - example blog post</a></h4>
                                        <p class="author-category">By <a href="#">John Slim</a> in <a href="">About Minimal</a>
                                        </p>
                                        <hr>
                                        <p class="intro">Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Vestibulum tortor quam, feugiat vitae, ultricies eget, tempor sit amet, ante. Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean
                                            ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo.</p>
                                        <p class="read-more"><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Continue reading</a>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {% block advantages %}
                        {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/Homepage/_advantages.html.twig') }}
                    {% endblock %}
                </div>
            {% endblock %}
        </div>

        <footer id="footer">
            <div class="container">
                {% block footer %}
                    {{ include('@SyliusWeb/Frontend/_footer.html.twig') }}
                {% endblock %}
            </div>
        </footer>
        <div id="copyright">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <p class="pull-left">
                        &#9400; 2016{% if ('now'|date('Y') != 2016) %} - {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} {% endif %}
                        BoardGameMonster is a trading name of Caponica Ltd.
                    </p>
                    <p class="pull-right">
                        <img src="{{ asset('img/payment.png') }}">
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        {% block javascripts %}
            {{ include('@SyliusWeb/_javascripts.html.twig') }}
        {% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>
